title: It Has To Go Back

description:
What you’re up against may seem permanent, but you have to remember, God has the final say. This is not how your story ends. The trouble may have formed, but it’s not going to prosper.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.
